Package ro.ubb.truckers.repository

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Repository<ID,​T extends BaseEntity<ID>>
    Interface for generic CRUD operations on a repository for a specific type.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    BaseRepository<ID,​T extends BaseEntity<ID>>
    The base for each type of repositories which contains the main implementation.
    FileRepository<ID,​T extends BaseEntity<ID>>
    The file repository keeps the data stored in txt files.
    MemoryRepository<ID,​T extends BaseEntity<ID>>
    The memory repository keeps the data stored in the memory and it is lost when stopping the code.
    RepositoryProvider
    Helps with feeding the application the selected repository by the user with ease.
